sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Server as Regex Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Registry as Detector Registry<br/>(HashMap)
    participant Engine as Regex Engine<br/>(finite automaton)

    Note over Orchestrator,Engine: Flow 1: Text Content Detection (PII / Custom Patterns)

    Orchestrator->>Server: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Body: {"contents": ["text..."], "detectors": {"email": {}, "ssn": {}, ...}}
    activate Server

    Server->>Registry: Look up detector names<br/>("email", "ssn", "credit-card", or custom regex)
    activate Registry

    alt Built-in Detector (e.g. "email", "ssn", "credit-card")
        Registry->>Engine: Apply pre-compiled regex pattern
    else Custom Regex Pattern
        Registry->>Engine: Compile and apply user-supplied regex
    end
    activate Engine

    Engine-->>Registry: Matches with character offsets
    deactivate Engine

    Registry-->>Server: Detection results<br/>[{start, end, detection_type, detection, score: 1.0}]
    deactivate Registry

    Server-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Body: [{"detections": [{start, end, text, detection_type, score}]}]
    deactivate Server

    Note over Orchestrator,Engine: Flow 2: Health Check

    Orchestrator->>Server: GET /health
    activate Server
    Server-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>Body: "healthy"
    deactivate Server
